

A simple and efficient tool to track your job applications — including company names, positions, application status, interview rounds, and notes — all in one place. Built to help job seekers stay organized during their job search journey.

---

## 🚀 Features

* 📋 Add, edit, and delete job applications
* 🔍 Filter and search applications by status or company
* 🗓️ Track application dates, interview stages, and follow-ups
* 🏷️ Custom tags for roles, industries, or priorities
* 📊 Dashboard overview (applied, interviewing, rejected, offered)
* ☁️ Optional: Save data locally or sync with a cloud database

